OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FWimbledon organisers are "surprised
OL,8,Fand disappointed" that leading tennis
OL,9,Fplayers will limit media interviews to
OL,10,F15 minutes in a dispute over prize
OL,11,Fmoney.
OL,13,FThe All England Club increased this
OL,14,Fyear's tournament pot by 20 per cent
OL,15,Fto #64.2million after some stars
OL,16,Fprotested at the French Open.
OL,18,FBut so-called player politics has been
OL,19,Fas hot a topic of discussion in the
OL,20,Ftennis world this season as forehands
OL,21,Fand backhands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
