OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782398899
OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FWorld number ones Aryna Sabalenka and
OL,8,FJannik Sinner are among 20 who will
OL,9,Fnot only limit the time they offer at
OL,10,Fthe forthcoming SW19 media weekend,
OL,11,Fthey also plan to restrict post-match
OL,12,Fappearances to 15 minutes throughout
OL,13,Fthe first week of the Championships,
OL,14,Fwhich start on Monday.
OL,16,FThe move is meant to symbolise the 15
OL,17,Fper cent of revenue which - broadly
OL,18,Fspeaking - the Grand Slams allocate to
OL,19,Fprize money.JWhat are the players
OL,20,Funhappy about?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
