OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FAt the top of the list is prize money.
OL,8,FThey argue the slams should pay a
OL,9,Fhigher percentage of revenue and have
OL,10,Falighted on reaching 22 per cent,
OL,11,Fwhich they say is broadly the figure
OL,12,Fon the ATP and WTA Tours, by 2030.
OL,14,FThey are also calling for
OL,15,Fcontributions from the slams to
OL,16,Fwelfare programmes, including pensions
OL,17,Fand a meaningful voice at the table.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
