OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FAhead of the French Open, they
OL,8,Freleased a statement expressing their
OL,9,Fdisappointment with a prize money
OL,10,Fincrease of only 9.5 per cent.
OL,12,FThey took their first direct action at
OL,13,FRoland Garros, limiting their pre-
OL,14,Fmatch media commitments to only 15
OL,15,Fminutes ` the approximate percentage
OL,16,Fof revenue paid by the French Open.
OL,18,FIn Paris, Sinner and Iga Swiatek - the
OL,19,F2025 Wimbledon women's singles
OL,20,Fchampion - followed the "work to rule"
OL,21,Fdirective
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
