OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FWhat was the impact?
OL,9,FThe players were emboldened by the
OL,10,Fresult.
OL,12,FThe protest immediately brought French
OL,13,FOpen organisers to the table, with the
OL,14,Fpromise of a concrete proposal to
OL,15,Ffollow, while further meetings
OL,16,Ffollowed with Wimbledon and US Open
OL,17,Fchiefs.
OL,19,FWhat about Wimbledon prize money?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
