OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FRarely has there been such scrutiny on
OL,8,Fa prize money announcement as there
OL,9,Fwas when Wimbledon held its spring
OL,10,Fpress conference earlier this month. T
OL,12,Fhe slams do not agree with the
OL,13,Fplayers' use of revenue as the sole
OL,14,Fmarker for prize money, but the 2026
OL,15,Ftotal was announced as #64.2million `
OL,16,Fa huge 20 per cent increase from 2025,
OL,17,Fthough still short of the 16 per cent
OL,18,Fof revenue demanded by the players for
OL,19,Fthis year.
OL,21,FWill there be further protests?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
