OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FThe players initially reacted
OL,8,Fpositively, describing the figure as a
OL,9,F"meaningful signal of intent".
OL,11,FWimbledon thought they had staved off
OL,12,Fthe threat of more action so it was
OL,13,Fsomething of a surprise to learn the
OL,14,Fplayers are not just repeating the
OL,15,FRoland Garros protest but amplifying
OL,16,Fit, with the 15-minute limit also
OL,17,Fapplied to post-match press in the
OL,18,Ffirst week of the tournament.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
