OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FThis will affect the tournament's
OL,8,Fpremium broadcast partners, including
OL,9,Fthe BBC, who may not be able to secure
OL,10,Ftheir usual interviews.
OL,12,FWhat happens next?
OL,14,FWimbledon had planned to meet with the
OL,15,Fplayers' representative Larry Scott
OL,16,Ffollowing the tournament, but this
OL,17,Flatest action has certainly increased
OL,18,Ftensions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
