OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FThe US Open will be the next
OL,8,Ftournament under scrutiny and, having
OL,9,Fupped its prize money by 20 per cent
OL,10,Flast year, another big rise will be
OL,11,Fexpected, particularly given the eye-
OL,12,Fwatering ticket prices.
OL,14,FThere has been talk of boycotting the
OL,15,Ftournament's big-money mixed doubles
OL,16,Fdraw, which was brought forward to the
OL,17,Fweek before the main event last year
OL,18,Fand attracted a star-studded field.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
