OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FAn All England Club spokesman said:
OL,8,F"We are surprised and disappointed by
OL,9,Fthis action.
OL,11,F"Wimbledon puts the players at the
OL,12,Fheart of all our decisions, and we
OL,13,Finvest significantly in them every
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,F"This year's total prize money fund
OL,17,Fhas increased by 20 per cent to #64.2
OL,18,Fmillion, which is the largest increase
OL,19,Fin our event's history.
OL,26,@pD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
