OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,F"This is alongside investing hundreds
OL,8,Fof millions of pounds in upgrades to
OL,9,Four player facilities as part of a
OL,10,Fthree-year transformation to create a
OL,11,Fworld-class player performance
OL,12,Fenvironment."
OL,14,FRepresentatives for players from the
OL,15,FATP and WTA Tours had described
OL,16,FWimbledon's prize money increase at
OL,17,Fthe time as "a genuine and significant
OL,18,Fstep forward" and "a meaningful signal
OL,19,Fof intent".
