OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FBut after detailed consultations with
OL,8,Fplayers, they have decided to extend
OL,9,Ftheir protests.
OL,11,FThey argue the current prize money
OL,12,Frepresents 14.4 per cent of projected
OL,13,Frevenues for the Championships, which
OL,14,Fis still below the 14.9 per cent
OL,15,Ffigure allocated in 2015.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
