OL,3,CWimbledon prize money protest: What
OL,4,Care the world's top players unhappy
OL,5,Cabout?
OL,7,FThe players had proposed the amount be
OL,8,Fraised to 16 per cent (#71.2m) as "a
OL,9,Fmeaningful interim step" towards their
OL,10,Fcalls for it to be lifted to 22 per
OL,11,Fcent ` in line with leading tour
OL,12,Fevents ` by 2030.
OL,14,FWimbledon chiefs branded that
OL,15,Fpercentage unrealistic because of the
OL,16,Fgreater responsibility they bear to
OL,17,Finvest in facilities and the wider
OL,18,Fgame, unlike other tour events.
OL,26,@pD@cOUqD@XO]
